==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inconcinnity
<hw>In`con*cin"ni*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inconcinnitas</ets>.]</ety> <def>Lack of concinnity or
congruousness; unsuitableness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There is an <qex>inconcinnity</qex> in admitting these words.</q>
<rj><qau>Trench.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inconcinnous</ent>⟦br⟧
